Description
What is Mad Octopus Diving Club?
We are Mad Octopus Diving Club 🐙 and we pioneer environmentally sustainable NFTs. 
WHY: Everyday 8 million plastic pieces pollute our oceans.🌊 
WHAT: Therefore we have created MODC to raise awareness for the problem and funds to donate to NGOs removing ocean plastic. 
HOW: 
70% of all proceeds through the NFT sale will be donated, 30% will be used for marketing and development cost. 
We are transparently communicating which NGOs we want to support and the holders of MODC NFTs are to decide what the split of donations to these NGOs will be. There are NGOs that accept donations in crypto, thus the donations will be transparent and visible on the blockchain. 
On top of that the environmental impact of each MODC will be stored on the blockchain as well, calculated through ETH prices at the moment of purchase as well as additional donations to the NFT which will increase the impact, backed by scientific papers on how much it costs to remove 1kg of plastic from the ocean. 
Holders and thus members of the Mad Octopus Diving Club will be eligble to: vote on the distribution of donations, receive giveaways like products made out of ocean plastic, participate in impact challenges to win prizes, and many more described in our roadmap.

Mars Genesis.name: Mars Genesis
Mars Genesis.description:
Description
What is Mars Genesis?
The Mars Genesis cards are "Non-Fungible Tokens" on Ethereum and ERC-721 standard that powers most digital art and collectibles.
No parcel has the same size or collection of attributes. Therefore, each has a different value. As a matter of fact, the topography, water data, temperature range, and colony conditions are accurate to the extent of human knowledge and from compiling state-of-the-art research.
Mars is finite. Therefore, once the 10,000 cards covering the planet are minted, the only way to acquire one is to purchase it from someone via the marketplace that is embedded in the blockchain. Via this market, you can buy, bid on, and offer cards for sale.
Each card represents a parcel of land on Mars with unique coordinates. These coordinates are part of the contract and define the unicity of a card. Therefore, and unlike any other NFT project, if for some obscure reasons, the IPFS (InterPlanetary File System) would go down, what makes your card unique and distinguishable would still live on the blockchain forever.
Each new card minted is generated randomly from the pool of remaining parcels. Prices start at 0.15 ETH and increase progressively to 0.5 ETH for the most expensive cards. For every trade on MarsGenesis marketplace, the first-owner of a card (minter) will receive a 4% royalty in perpetuity.

NEWMetasplit.name: NEWMetasplit
NEWMetasplit.description:
Description
What is Metasplit?
The more the market of NFT and metaverses grows, the more prices increase. And most people can't afford to buy land on the metaverse anymore because of this price increase. In the real world, this problem has been partially solved by allowing people to join together and buy a property through a company for example. This is exactly what Metasplit is intended for!
Metasplit allows several people to become co-owner of a land (i.e. NFT) while staying entirely compatible with the ERC721 and ERC1155 standards, thus allowing to interface with any platform respecting these standards. Each co-owner has a shares of land proportionally to his contribution. And each co-owner is free to sell on our exchange the number of shares he wants at the price that suits him.
Metasplit is a NFT's tokenization and ownership delegation protocol opening the way to crowdfunding, decentralized trading and many other features.

Each mASSET is a liquidity share for its asset pool as well as a medium of exchange, unit of account and store of value in its own right. Each mASSET has an outsized native interest rate that is derived from lending basket assets on third party lending protocols combined with fees collected from mStable's SWAP product. Users can swap between basket assets with zero price slippage, regardless of order size. For example, in mUSD, users are able to swap 1 DAI for 1 USDC at no cost, except gas and a small fee.

MurAll.name: MurAll
MurAll.description:
Description
What is MurAll?
MurAll is a collaborative canvas allowing artists worldwide to paint onto an ever evolving piece of art. This is a first of its kind project made possible by the use of blockchain technology.
Powered by the Ethereum network, MurAll requires a digital token called PAINT to enable artists to draw onto the canvas. Each PAINT token can draw 2 pixels and just like real-life paint, it can only be used to draw once. If it has been used it can’t be taken off of the wall and reused! 
With only a finite amount of PAINT available globally (there is only enough PAINT to cover the canvas 21,000 times), it is a commodity that encourages artists to produce work they are passionate about as the more PAINT that is used, the less is available.
Once an artist has created their piece and “minted” it on the MurAll canvas, it is immortalised forever on the blockchain. The artist receives an NFT (Non Fungible Token) of their drawing; in contrast to traditional tokens, NFTs are one of a kind, ensuring that the artwork is a UNIQUE ORIGINAL which has value and can be kept or sold whenever they wish - just like real-life paintings. Unlike most existing technologies, the artwork itself is contained within the token and isn't just a certificate.

Gifts for Deposit and Withdrawal! ? Guaranteed refund at least 70% of the initial deposit in any case and regardless of the duration of your participation! HOW IT WORKS? 1. You save your deposit. Then just lie on your couch and watch how an amount of your Savings grows in value in each new time interval (Pack). If you are a new participant, then 60% of your initial amount is immediately returned to the balance of your wallet! In addition, the System compensates a part of the transaction fee! The amount of your savings will be increased by approximately 10% after closure of the second pack of your participation and will continue increasing by approximately 43% after closure of each subsequent pack. The more participants in the System and the greater the amount of their savings — the faster the System moves on to the following packs. 2. You make a withdrawal. Do you want to withdraw your savings in full or in part? No problem! At any time and without any restrictions! You are always able to withdraw 70-100% of your initial savings amount.
